# Blackjack

A JavaFX-based Blackjack game where you play against an AI opponent.

## Features
- Interactive card UI with real card images
- Draw cards or hold your hand
- AI opponent that automatically draws after you hold
- Clean JavaFX interface

## Technologies
- Java
- JavaFX
- Maven

## How to Play
- Draw cards to get as close to 21 as possible
- Press **Hold** to stop drawing – the AI will then play automatically
- Whoever is closest to 21 without going over wins
